This is a simple shopping cart website that allows users to view a list of available products, add items to their cart, and remove items from their cart.

Features

Display a list of available products with their name and description
Add items to the cart by clicking the "Add to Cart" button
Increase the cart quantity number when an item is added to the cart
Change the "Add to Cart" button to the "Remove from Cart" button once the item is added to the cart
Remove items from the cart by clicking the "Remove from Cart" button
Decrease the cart quantity number when an item is removed from the cart
Change the "Remove from Cart" button back to the "Add to Cart" button once the item is removed from the cart
Technical Details

Built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript
Uses a simple cart system to store and manage cart items
No backend or database is required for this website
How to Use

Open the website in a web browser
View the list of available products
Click the "Add to Cart" button to add an item to the cart
Click the "Remove from Cart" button to remove an item from the cart
View the cart quantity number to see the number of items in the cart
Code Structure

index.html: The main HTML file for the website
style.css: The CSS file for styling the website
script.js: The JavaScript file for handling cart functionality
